descriptionTemplates.patch_cycle:
Apply {platform} security patches for {patchCycle}.

Affected Systems: {assetCount} assets
Severity: {severity}
First Detected: {firstDetected}
SLA Breach Date: {breachDate}

This POAM consolidates {findingCount} findings that require the {patchCycle} patch cycle to be applied.

Sample CVEs: {sampleCVEs}
