SLA Breach Date: {breachDate}

This POAM consolidates {findingCount} findings across multiple CVEs that are all resolved by upgrading {component} to the latest approved version.

Sample CVEs: {sampleCVEs}
Sample Advisories: {sampleAdvisories}

